# Implementation Plan - ModEx

ModEx is a modern, desktop-based Minecraft mod manager focused on organization, bulk importing, and modpack management.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech Stack Change**: Switched from React to **Vue.js** as requested.
> **UI Library**: Will use **Shadcn-vue** (or compatible Vue equivalent like Radix-Vue + Tailwind) to maintain the requested premium aesthetic.

## Proposed Changes

### Project Structure
