### Backend (Electron/Node)
#### [NEW] [Background Services](file:///c:/Users/zagor/Desktop/modex/electron/main)
- `main.ts`: Entry point, window creation.
- `preload.ts`: IPC bridge for safe communication.
- `database.ts`: SQLite connection and schema management using `better-sqlite3` or `drizzle-orm`.
- `scanner.ts`: Logic to recursively scan directories for `.jar` files and extract metadata (using `adm-zip` to read `mcmod.info` or `fabric.mod.json`).

### Frontend (Vue.js)
#### [NEW] [UI Components](file:///c:/Users/zagor/Desktop/modex/src/components)
- **Layout**: Sidebar navigation, top bar with search.
- **ModGrid**: Grid view of mod cards with images/icons.
- **Filters**: Faceted search (Game Version, Loader, Genre).
- **Importer**: Drag & drop zone or file picker for bulk import.

#### [NEW] [Views](file:///c:/Users/zagor/Desktop/modex/src/views)
- `LibraryView.vue`: Main list of all imported mods.
- `ModpackView.vue`: Management of modpacks (create, edit, assign mods).
- `SettingsView.vue`: Path configurations.

### Database Schema
- **Mods**: `id`, `filename`, `name`, `version`, `game_version`, `loader`, `path`, `hash`.
- **Modpacks**: `id`, `name`, `version`, `description`.
- **Modpack_Mods**: Join table `modpack_id`, `mod_id`.
- **Tags/Categories**: Dynamic categorization.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Unit tests for the `scanner` logic (parsing sample jars).
- Component tests for Vue components.

### Manual Verification
- **Import Flow**: Drag 10+ jar files -> Verify they appear in DB with correct metadata.
- **Organization**: Create a "Survival" modpack -> Add mods -> Verify association.
- **UI Check**: Verify "premium" feel (animations, dark mode, responsiveness).
